ğŸ“Œ ##Project Overview

This project demonstrates a complete CI/CD pipeline that automatically builds, pushes, and deploys a containerized web application to a self-managed Kubernetes cluster using Jenkins.

Whenever code is pushed to the develop branch on GitHub, Jenkins:

Builds a Docker image

Pushes it to Docker Hub

Deploys the updated image to Kubernetes (staging environment)

ğŸ§° Tech Stack

Version Control: GitHub

CI/CD Tool: Jenkins

Containerization: Docker

Container Registry: Docker Hub

Orchestration: Kubernetes (Self-managed, not EKS)

Web Server: Nginx / Apache

OS: Linux (EC2)

