kubectl logs <pod-name> -n staging

ğŸ¯ Key Learnings

Jenkins pipeline design using declarative syntax

Secure credential handling in CI/CD

Docker image versioning and registry integration

Kubernetes deployments using kubectl

End-to-end automation from GitHub to Kubernetes

